snippet.title: OUTER WILDS | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to PC and Xbox One. http://outerwilds.com

Steam: http://bit.ly/OuterWildsSteam
Epic: http://bit.ly/OuterWildsEpic
Xbox: http://bit.ly/OuterWildsXbox

Outer Wilds is an open world mystery about a solar system trapped in an endless time loop. 

Developed by MOBIUS DIGITAL. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2018
